Štai pakartotiniai dešimtainiai trupmenos $0.\dot{3}$, $0.\dot{2}\dot{4}$ ir $42.34\dot{7}\dot{8}$ konvertuotos i paprastuosius trupmenos.
\vspace{-1em}
\begin{small}
\begin{centerpage}{0.9\textwidth}
\begin{align*} 
\text{Pirma \qquad}0.\dot{3} &= 0,3333 \ldots \\
0.\dot{3} \times 10 = 0,333 \ldots \times 10 &= 3,333 \ldots\\
0.\dot{3} \times 1 = 0,333 \ldots \times 1 &= 0,333 \ldots\\[-1em]\cline{1-2}
\text{atimdami, }0.\dot{3} \times 10 - 0.\dot{3} \times 1 &=3\\
0.\dot{3} \times (10-1) &= 3\\  
0.\dot{3} \times 9&=3\\
